#: ../extras/chat.rst:62
msgid "Creating a Ticket from a Chat"
msgstr "Jegy létrehozása csevegésből"

#: ../extras/chat.rst:64
msgid ""
"Once your chat is over, you can create a ticket for it with a single click:"
